snippet.title: Can You Fool A Self Driving Car?
snippet.description:
Never underestimate the power of freakin' lasers! Have fun learning to think like an engineer and get 2 FREE boxes at: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

Get your CrunchLabs box today:
Build Box for kids click here: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar
Hack Pack for teens and adults click here: http://crunchlabs.com/LidarHP

Full un-cut footage from the fake wall crash: https://x.com/MarkRober/status/1901449395327094898 s=46

Thanks to Luminar for allowing us to test their LiDAR-equipped car. They provided the vehicle for testing purposes, but no compensation was given, and this is not a paid promotion: https://www.luminartech.com/

en.title: Can You Fool A Self Driving Car?
en.description:
Never underestimate the power of freakin' lasers! Have fun learning to think like an engineer and get 2 FREE boxes at: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

Get your CrunchLabs box today:
Build Box for kids click here: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar
Hack Pack for teens and adults click here: http://crunchlabs.com/LidarHP

Full un-cut footage from the fake wall crash: https://x.com/MarkRober/status/1901449395327094898 s=46


Thanks to Harrison @IndianaDrones from Rock Robotic for helping with his very cool lidar. You can check out scans from the project and a 3d tour of CrunchLabs by visiting  https://www.rockrobotic.com/

Thanks to Luminar for allowing us to test their LiDAR-equipped car. They provided the vehicle for testing purposes, but no compensation was given, and this is not a paid promotion: https://www.luminartech.com/

Thanks to these folks for providing some of the music in the video:

snippet.title: Chaotic 4x400 caps men's 2025 NCAA indoor championship
snippet.description:
Watch all three sections of the men's 4x400m final â€”Â and the lengthy delay/review that followed â€” at the 2025 NCAA indoor track and field championships. Southern California won the 2025 Division I men's indoor track and field title, clinching the title with the meets final event â€” the chaotic 4x400 meter relay. Texas A&M got disqualified for flagrantly impeding Arkansas, which campaigned for a re-run of the race but was denied.

After the dust settled, USC outpaced Arkansas to score five points in the 4x4 to give the Trojans the championship win by six points. In total, USC finished with 39 points, while Georgia finished with 33 points in second place. It's USC's first men's indoor title in 53 years.

Subscribe to the NCAA Championship YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/NCAAChampionships?sub_confirmation=1

Get your NCAA Championship tickets here: https://www.ncaatickets.com/

snippet.title: Kingdom Come Deliverance 2 IS A PERFECTLY BALANCED GAME WITH NO EXPLOITS
snippet.description:
KCD2 Is here and it is rapidly becoming one of the greatest RPGs of all time! Of course as a fan of open world sandbox rpgs like skyrim I am drawn to the adventure that kingdom come deliverance has to offer. Of course similar to your average elder scrolls game the developers have left in some perfectly balanced game design choices that might result in the spiffing brit having to ask an important question. Is Kingdom Come Deliverance 2 A Perfectly balanced game with no exploits? Or perhaps are there bugs, glitches and overpowered features that spiff can use to turn himself into a god. 

What you have seen here today is part of a fantastic perfectly balanced gameplay series on youtube where I go from game to game and break them with wacky exploits to gain things like unlimited gold and infinite money all in a fantastic montage. If you enjoyed this then be sure to check out more. The style is similar to RT game and callmekevin in parts. A large influence on this series has come from Valefisk and The Killian Experience.

02:58 Let Him Cook

snippet.title: Finally! US is Testing Brand New B-52s To Fly For A Full Century!
snippet.description:
When the B-52 Stratofortress made its first flight in 1952, no one could have imagined that this bomber would survive not only the Cold War, but the turn of the century, as well!
Today, more than 70 years later, it not only remains in service, but is also undergoing another modernization that can ensure its combat effectiveness for several more decades!
Now letâ€™s take a look at how an ordinary turboprop project from the mid-20th century became a symbol of the strategic power of the 21st century!

Today, more than 70 years later, it not only remains in service, but is also undergoing another modernization that can ensure its combat effectiveness for several more decades!
Now letâ€™s take a look at how an ordinary turboprop project from the mid-20th century became a symbol of the strategic power of the 21st century!

snippet.title: Blastoff! NASA's SpaceX Crew-10 launches to space station, booster lands in Florida
snippet.description:
A SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket launched the Crew-10 mission for NASA from Launch Complex-39 at the Kennedy Space Center (KSC) in Florida on March 14, 2025 at 7:03 p.m. EST (2348 GMT). Full Story: https://www.space.com/space-exploration/international-space-station/spacex-launches-relief-crew-for-nasas-beleaguered-starliner-astronauts-on-iss-video

Crew-10 is NASA astronauts Anne McClain and Nichole Ayers, JAXA (Japan Aerospace Exploration Agency) astronaut Takuya Onishi and Roscosmos cosmonaut Kirill Peskov. 

Credit: NASA

snippet.title: An Exquisitely Unusual Tiny Home Built With Natureâ€™s Geometry
snippet.description:
This is a tiny house that immediately captured my heart. There's something about the curved roof, the stained glass windows and the rounded doors that remind me of a modern hobbit-like home that just radiates warmth, character and comfort. 

Philippa is a remarkable woman. I enjoyed my time with her immensely. I can always tell when I meet a kindred spirit and I felt this way with her. You know that when you meet a person who can talk with penguins, you've met someone very special indeed. She has lived a big life and done some remarkable things, One of those things is building her tiny house. A very bespoke home that sings to her soul. 

And this home! Beautiful and character filled. It's enough, and yet it's so much more. From the beautiful shapes and all the wonderful adornments this is a house that radiates a very real sensation of home. 

Nature has very few right angles, and that trait is shared with this tiny home. A true labour of love for Philippa and her builders, this is a tiny house not to be forgotten. Crafted with sacred geometric principles in mind, this could very easily be your new favourite tiny home. We very much hope you enjoy the tour. 

You can find out more about Philippa, her writing and links to listen to her podcast via her website: https://philippaross.com

If you enjoy our show and would like to help support our work, please consider supporting us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/livingbig

Our Socials and Links: https://linktr.ee/livingbig

Find out more about this tiny house and others on our website: https://www.livingbiginatinyhouse.com/

id.title: Rumah Mungil yang Luar Biasa dan Unik yang Dibangun dengan Geometri Alam
id.description:
Ini adalah rumah mungil yang langsung menarik hati saya. Ada sesuatu tentang atap melengkung, jendela kaca patri, dan pintu bundar yang mengingatkan saya pada rumah modern mirip hobbit yang memancarkan kehangatan, karakter, dan kenyamanan. 

Philippa adalah wanita yang luar biasa. Saya sangat menikmati waktu saya bersamanya. Saya selalu tahu ketika saya bertemu dengan jiwa yang sama dan saya merasakan hal ini bersamanya. Anda tahu bahwa ketika Anda bertemu seseorang yang dapat berbicara dengan penguin, Anda telah bertemu seseorang yang sangat istimewa. Dia telah menjalani kehidupan yang hebat dan melakukan beberapa hal yang luar biasa. Salah satunya adalah membangun rumah mungilnya. Rumah yang sangat dipesan khusus yang bernyanyi bagi jiwanya. 

Dan rumah ini! Indah dan penuh karakter. Itu cukup, namun masih jauh lebih dari itu. Dari bentuknya yang indah dan semua hiasan yang indah, ini adalah rumah yang memancarkan sensasi rumah yang sangat nyata. 

Alam memiliki sangat sedikit sudut siku-siku, dan sifat itu juga dimiliki oleh rumah mungil ini. Sebuah karya cinta sejati bagi Philippa dan para pembangunnya, ini adalah rumah mungil yang tak terlupakan. Dibuat dengan prinsip-prinsip geometri suci, ini bisa dengan mudah menjadi rumah mungil favorit baru Anda. Kami sangat berharap Anda menikmati tur ini.

Anda dapat mengetahui lebih lanjut tentang Philippa, tulisannya, dan tautan untuk mendengarkan podcastnya melalui situs webnya: https://philippaross.com

Jika Anda menikmati acara kami dan ingin membantu mendukung pekerjaan kami, mohon pertimbangkan untuk mendukung kami di Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/livingbig

Media Sosial dan Tautan Kami: https://linktr.ee/livingbig

Cari tahu lebih lanjut tentang rumah mungil ini dan lainnya di situs web kami: https://www.livingbiginatinyhouse.com/

snippet.title: Kevin Hart Celebrates 10 Years of Hot Ones While Eating Spicy Wings | Hot Ones
snippet.description:
On March 12, 2015, Hot Ones premiered to the world with Sean Evans serving up hot questions and even hotter wings for Tony Yayo. Now, we celebrate the show's 10th anniversary with one of the giants of Hot Ones history, Kevin Hart. He's an actor, producer, director, and entrepreneuerâ€”not to mention one of the most successful stand-up comedians of all time. Check out the animated series based on his childhood, Lil Kev, now streaming on BET+, as well as his tequila Gran Coramino, and a new two-part documentary film called Number One on the Call Sheet, which premieres on Apple TV March 28th. But how is he with spicy food? Find out as the man who proclaimed "what y'all got going on here is genius!" when he first appeared on the show takes on the wings of death and discusses his beloved Philadelphia Eagles, action-movie stunts gone wrong, and the impact of Hot Ones on media. Thanks for rocking with us for a decade, Spice Lords!

In June 2025, the game enters a new era with Siege X, the biggest and most transformative evolution in its history. This milestone will bring a visual overhaul, an enhanced player experience and gameplay changes that deepen the gameâ€™s tactical core.

Learn more: https://www.rainbow6.com/SiegeX

Rainbow Six Siege is available now on Xbox, PlayStationÂ® and PC.

en.title: Rainbow Six Siege X Reveal Gameplay Trailer
en.description:
The biggest evolution Rainbow Six Siege has ever seen! Watch livestreams to get BETA access, from March 13 to 19.

In June 2025, the game enters a new era with Siege X, the biggest and most transformative evolution in its history. This milestone will bring a visual overhaul, an enhanced player experience and gameplay changes that deepen the gameâ€™s tactical core.

Learn more: https://www.rainbow6.com/SiegeX

Music by Ark of Noah, Y2 performing Walk Through The Fire

Access to the game is free; certain features, including competitive game modes, operators, and cosmetics, require payment to unlock

About Rainbow Six Siege:
Rainbow Six Siege is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege is available now on Xbox, PlayStationÂ® and PC.

#Ubisoft #R6Siege 

About Ubisoft:
Ubisoft is a creator of worlds, committed to enriching playersâ€™ lives with original and memorable entertainment experiences. Ubisoftâ€™s global teams create and develop a deep and diverse portfolio of games, featuring brands such as Assassinâ€™s CreedÂ®, BrawlhallaÂ®, For HonorÂ®, Far CryÂ®, Tom Clancyâ€™s Ghost ReconÂ®, Just DanceÂ®, RabbidsÂ®, Tom Clancyâ€™s Rainbow SixÂ®, The CrewÂ® and Tom Clancyâ€™s The DivisionÂ®. Through Ubisoft Connect, players can enjoy an ecosystem of services to enhance their gaming experience, get rewards and connect with friends across platforms. With Ubisoft+, the subscription service, they can access a growing catalog of more than 100 Ubisoft games and DLC. For the 2023-24 fiscal year, Ubisoft generated net bookings of â‚¬2.32 billion. To learn more, please visit: www.ubisoftgroup.com.

Welcome to the Heavy Spoilers show, I'm your host Paul and this video we're breaking down Invincible.

0:45

Season 3 is now at an end but episode 8 has a lot going on. We're calling it Glenns revenge. This includes a gigantic battle and also a massive tease for the future. That post credit scenes all completely new and we have some theories for that too.

Where the main focus is though is with Conquest Vs Mark. Starting right in at the title we pick up where we left off last week. That title at the start means we're diving right into it and we see punch play out. It's completely earth shattering and the shockwaves a big way to kick off the fight. Mentioning Anissa sales pitch Conquest says the the truth is that he wants him to resist.

This is almost beat for beat...for beat like how it is in the comics with them perfectly recapturing the fight. If you wanna dive into the books then you need to pick up issue 62. From here if you work to 65 you'll have basically the outline of the comics.

Most of the episode is one to one, however they change up a lot of moments of the dialogue.

Conquest is voiced by Jeffrey Dean Morgan which is such a great fourth wall breaking moment. Thats because both him and Steven Yeun worked with Kirkman on The Walking Dead.

Welcome to the Heavy Spoilers show, I'm your host Paul and this video we're breaking down Invincible.

0:45

Season 3 is now at an end but episode 8 has a lot going on. We're calling it Glenns revenge. This includes a gigantic battle and also a massive tease for the future. That post credit scenes all completely new and we have some theories for that too.

Where the main focus is though is with Conquest Vs Mark. Starting right in at the title we pick up where we left off last week. That title at the start means we're diving right into it and we see punch play out. It's completely earth shattering and the shockwaves a big way to kick off the fight. Mentioning Anissa sales pitch Conquest says the the truth is that he wants him to resist.

This is almost beat for beat...for beat like how it is in the comics with them perfectly recapturing the fight. If you wanna dive into the books then you need to pick up issue 62. From here if you work to 65 you'll have basically the outline of the comics.

Most of the episode is one to one, however they change up a lot of moments of the dialogue.

Conquest is voiced by Jeffrey Dean Morgan which is such a great fourth wall breaking moment. Thats because both him and Steven Yeun worked with Kirkman on The Walking Dead.

snippet.title: SIDEMEN CHARITY MATCH 2025 [OFFICIAL STREAM]
snippet.description:
Sidemen Charity Match 2025

Donate here: https://www.sidemenfc.com 

On the 8th of March Sidemen FC and YouTube Allstars are coming together to play the 2025 Charity Match at Wembley Stadium.

Use the hashtag #SDMNCharityMatch to talk about the game!

OFFICIAL STREAM starts at 2:10pm GMT

Kick off time is at 3pm GMT

The Sidemen Charity Match 2025 is in aid of the following charities and funds raised will be split as follows:

Bright Side 43%
BBC Children in Need 50%
M7 Education 7%

We will also donate all of the profit we make through the match and related activities to the following charities:

Bright Side 86%
M7 Education 14%

Any donations you make are greatly appreciated and going to great causes! We hope you enjoy the match.

For full details and terms and conditions please visit https://sidemenfc.com.

Viewers of this livestream are strictly prohibited from re-streaming or rebroadcasting this content on any platform. Any unauthorised re-streaming will result in the immediate removal of the infringing livestream and a copyright strike issued to the violator.

snippet.title: Team TaylorMade SWAPS Drivers For A Straightest Drive Contest...
snippet.description:
Team TaylorMade is back together and in this video, they're going to be switching Qi35 Drivers and competing in a straightest drive competition. 

Each person will walk around the bags while music plays and when the music stops, they have to hit whoever's driver they land on. The two golfers who hit it most off-line will be eliminated, and the last golfer standing wins. 

This all shows why it's so important to get fit for a Qi35 Driver that is optimized for YOUR game. 

Tiger Woods is MC, and Scottie Scheffler, Nelly Korda, Rory McIlroy, Collin Morikawa, Tommy Fleetwood, Charley Hull, and Brooke Henderson are playing. Watch till the end for a special surprise from Tiger.

snippet.title: Path of Exile 2: Dawn of the Hunt Teaser
snippet.description:
In two weeks tune in to twitch.tv/pathofexile to get all the information about our next content update for Path of Exile 2! 

During the livestream you'll learn all about the 0.2.0 content update for Path of Exile 2. After the livestream, Jonathan and Mark will answer your burning questions live in a Q&A session with ZiggyD, which we will follow up with the full 0.2.0 patch notes.

You'll be able to play the 0.2.0 content update on PC and Consoles on April 4th (PDT). We are very excited to show you what we've been working on!

Baylee sings a song he wrote called "Waiting On Myself To Die" and gets high praise from Carrie Underwood, Luke Bryan, and Lionel Richie. Then an unexpected duet happens between Baylee and his Dad Brian! Backstreet's Back, ALRIGHT...and gets a golden ticket to Hollywood!

snippet.title: Sir Jim Ratcliffe: Amorim, Ten Hag, Finances & The Glazers | The Overlap With Gary Neville
snippet.description:
Gary Neville is joined by Sir Jim Ratcliffe on The Overlap, brought to you by Sky Bet. They discuss Manchester Unitedâ€™s season so far, new manager Ruben Amorim, the clubâ€™s finances, and whatâ€™s next for United.

Ratcliffe reflects on his first year at United, including the controversial decision to replace Erik ten Hag with Ruben Amorim, despite an FA Cup triumph. He also tackles the clubâ€™s financial struggles, including a bloated wage bill, and the steps being taken to bring United back to the top.

The conversation also lifts the lid on Dan Ashworthâ€™s departure, what really happened behind the scenes, and how it impacted Unitedâ€™s plans heading into a crucial second half of the Premier League season.

Looking ahead, Gary and Sir Jim discuss the future of Old Trafford, the clubâ€™s long-term vision, and whether United fans can find reasons for optimism after a below-par campaign.

Donâ€™t miss this oneâ€”hit like, share your thoughts in the comments, and subscribe to stay updated with every episode!

snippet.title: Finding A Player Who Doesn't Exist
snippet.description:
I received a message on discord from someone asking if I could help them find a friend they hadn't spoken with in a while. The task seemed innocent enough at first, but ended up being one of the most mysterious and darkest rabbit holes I've ever investigated. What happened to Alex? This is finding a minecraft player who doesn't exist.

Channel: @xXCraftykinggXx 

â¤â¤ Twitter: https://twitter.com/WifiesWasTaken
â¤â¤ Discord: https://discord.gg/zAWUuWb


â¤â¤Links: I dont think any? but maybe I'm forgetting 


This is a series called Minecraft VVSauce where I explore random features of Minecraft. Not Secret Minecraft things or Minecraft lore (like Game Theory) or Escape Rooms, but a scary arg based series. The footage in this video isn't of a real person, an ARG is a story that's known to be fictional but we all pretend it's real and try to solve the mystery that the owner of this channel created. Such is the life of an ARG hunter. Very scary very creepy. BOO!

snippet.title: Hiking To The CIAâ€™s â€œTop Secretâ€ Plane Crash in Death Valley
snippet.description:
Check out the best electrolyte mix out there at https://drinklmnt.com/Brent for a FREE 8-count sample pack! I take LMNT everywhere with me, especially on these long hikes.

In this video, I finally attempt a hike to the legendary crashed CIA plane in the middle of Death Valley. 

This plane was part of a top secret program in the 1950s as part of the United State's Cold War efforts. The program was a joint program between the Air Force and the CIA. Unfortunately, on one cold night in January of 1952, one of these planes crashed on a training mission over Death Valley. 

Due to the remote and difficult nature of getting to the airplane, it was left there. Now, 73 years later, I hiked in to see what it was all about!

I hope you enjoy!

You can follow my journey on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/brentwunderwood/

Cerro Gordo T-Shirts and more: https://store.cerrogordomines.com/ 

Mailing Address: PO Box 490, Lone Pine, CA 93545

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. Itâ€™s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX â€” interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything â€” be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer â€œCapture the Flagâ€ game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: SHOULD YOU TOW WITH A CYBERTRUCK?! - (catastrophic failure test)
snippet.description:
The Tesla Cybertruck is built with a cast aluminum frame. Get up to 40% off your RIDGE wallet here: https://www.ridge.com/JERRYRIG (discount code: JerryRig) Huge thanks to RIDGE for sponsoring my science projects. This helps the cyber truck be manufactured extremely quickly. However - cast aluminum is not good for towing as we see in this Cybertruck durability test video. The hitch breaks around 10,000 pounds. (4500kg) Which is far too close to the 11,000 pound towing capacity. Yikes. 

While the Gigacasting method is *terrible* for the Cybertruck it is actually an amazing manufacturing process for Tesla's other vehicles which i highly recommend: https://ts.la/zack10701

If you want an electric truck that can still tow 11,000lbs and not snap in half - might i recommend a Rivian: https://rivian.com/configurations/list?reprCode=ZACK1594426

Get up to 40% off your RIDGE wallet here: https://www.ridge.com/JERRYRIG (discount code: JerryRig) Huge thanks to RIDGE for sponsoring my science projects. This helps the cyber truck be manufactured extremely quickly. However - cast aluminum is not good for towing as we see in this Cybertruck durability test video. The hitch breaks around 10,000 pounds. (4500kg) Which is far too close to the 11,000 pound towing capacity. Yikes. 

While the Gigacasting method is *terrible* for the Cybertruck it is actually an amazing manufacturing process for Tesla's other vehicles which i highly recommend: https://ts.la/zack10701

If you want an electric truck that can still tow 11,000lbs and not snap in half - might i recommend a Rivian: https://rivian.com/configurations/list?reprCode=ZACK1594426

snippet.title: We Lived in a Truck Camper for 72 Hours
snippet.description:
A very Aussie 4x4 adventure on Stradbroke "Straddie" Island. Filmed Feb 10-13, 2025. Go to http://DrinkLMNT.com/eamonandbec for a free sample pack with any purchase!

After living in a converted sprinter van for nearly 5 years we thought we'd cracked the code to tiny house on wheels with #vanlife  But, this week we really test ourselves with a brand new setup... a 4X4 truck with a rooftop tent. Not only is it the smallest setup we've ever traveled in but we've also added our 1 year old daughter to the mix. Frankie is such an incredibly adaptable baby but can we really enjoy all that Australia has to offer with a 1 year old child in tow? 

We spot kangaroos, drive a 4X4 rig on some of Australia's most epic beaches and manage to keep up with our mate @MaxandOccy . Make sure you check out his episode for more of our adventures.

Originally from Nashville, Tennessee, we got married 2013 and were super â€œnormal.â€ I was a teacher and Nate started a small printing business from the spare bedroom of our apartment. 

We discovered the world of â€œtravel hackingâ€ while planning our honeymoon & became addicted ;)

So after 2 years of obsessively saving $35k and over 2 million miles and points, we sold our cars and apartment and left home January 10, 2016 for a â€œone yearâ€ trip around the world.

Our goal was to see as many places as possible before we ran out of money and went back home to â€œnormal life.â€ We started this channel to share our experiences with friends and family, but quickly fell in love with living on the road and found a new passion for capturing our travels through video. So we did everything we could to keep going.

4 years later, we achieved our new goal of visiting 100 countries and all 7 continents. We had no plans to slow down, until 2020 forced us to ;) Which is when we bought a converted van to start exploring our own country for the first time!

After ~2 years of van life, we are back to full time international traveling! And now we are in our 10TH YEAR of finding the best adventures the world has to offer :) 

We are incredibly grateful to be able to continue doing something we love every day. ğŸ˜ŠğŸ¥ğŸŒ Thank you to everyone who has been a part of our journey!

snippet.title: Squishy Makeovers  Fixing Your Squishies #38
snippet.description:
Welcome to another episode of squishy makeovers, where I transform ugly, used, old, dirty, cheap or unwanted squishies (donated by my subscribers) into my own creations. I repair, paint and cut away for hours on end to complete these. Hopefully you like them. Get used to lots of rainbow and sprinkles, because I am addicted to both!

Don't forget to check out the CHESS SET!
https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/

What I'm Using (contains affiliate links):
Squishy Makeovers Fixing Your Squishies #37
Tulip Matte Fabric Paint: https://amzn.to/49OjdMp
Tulip Slick Fabric Paint: https://amzn.to/3LBW6uO
Posca Pens: https://amzn.to/40TgXPL
Scissors: https://amzn.to/3MjSY6L
Sandpaper: https://amzn.to/3EQOOPY
Fabric Hot Glue: https://amzn.to/3PQ4KZh


_______FAQs________

1. CAN I SEND YOU SQUISHIES?
So many generous people have sent me their unwanted squishies so I actually have a lot to work on already, BUT if you desperately want to, you can request my mailing address in the email ALLLL the way at down in the description (sorry for the traveling), make sure to read the disclaimer down there as well.

2. ARE SQUISHIES RETURNED TO THE SENDERS AFTER THE MAKEOVER?
No. These squishies  are sent as donations to the series because they are damaged and/or no longer wanted. Everyone has been informed in advance that squishies would not be returned. 

3. WHAT PAINT DO YOU USE?
I use fabric paint. Fabric paint is meant to stretch, so it is perfect for squishing! Any brand will work fine, but I mainly use Tulip. You can find it at Michaels, Hobby Lobby, A.C. Moore, Walmart, Joann Fabrics, and Online.

5. WILL FABRIC PAINT CRACK?
